oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Raul Malo at Ace of Clubs
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Malo, Raul; Split fountain printing; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (split fountain, green to red, on white) announcing Raul Malo at the Ace of Clubs on December 19. Poster features a woodcut of a club, one of the suits in a deck of playing cards.
